Title: Sex, Lies and Larvae
Plot: Grissom and Sara investigate a bug-riddled body found in the desert. Warrick and Catherine look into the theft of valuable art. Nick investigates when a missing woman's car is found at a bus station. Warrick is suspected of having gambled on duty.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: John Getz, Mark Moses, Jennifer Sommerfield, Blake Lidsley, Lisa Arturo, Todd Sible, Jason Padgett, Josh Bastien, Alex Rice, Will Potter, Susan Santiago, Jennefer Toffel
